# Auto Git Sync

This project auto-pushes to `https://github.com/Cookie2124/ai-coach` via a Cursor **stop hook** (`.cursor/hooks/auto-push.mjs`).

When you finish making code changes in this repo:

1. Do **not** manually commit or push unless the user explicitly asks for a custom commit message or branch.
2. Ensure `.env` and other secrets stay out of git (never stage `.env`).
3. Leave the working tree with intentional changes only — the stop hook commits and pushes to `origin/main` when the agent session ends.

If the user asks to push immediately (before the session ends), run:

```powershell
git add -A
git -c user.email="Cookie2124@users.noreply.github.com" -c user.name="Cookie2124" commit -m "your message"
git push origin main
```
